<h2>What to Expect During a Session</h2>

<p>
A typical session lasts between 60 and 90 minutes. The chamber gradually pressurizes, and you may feel mild ear pressure similar to ascending in an airplane. You can relax, read, or rest during the session before it slowly depressurizes.
</p>

<h2>Price Range and Investment</h2>

<p>
The cost of a soft shell hyperbaric chamber typically ranges from <strong>$5,000 to $15,000</strong>, depending on size, brand, pressure rating, and included accessories.
</p>

<h2>Final Thoughts</h2>

<p>
Purchasing a soft shell hyperbaric chamber is a significant decision that requires careful research. From understanding pressure levels and safety features to comparing warranties and support, evaluating your options ensures you make the right choice.
</p>

<p>
With proper guidance and consistent use, a soft shell hyperbaric chamber can become a valuable addition to your wellness routine.
</p>

